import { FTypo, FGrid, FTable, FHeader } from "ferrum-design-system";
import Datatable from "react-bs-datatable";

import './layout.scss';

export const Withdrawals = () => {
    const tableHeads: any[] = [
        { width: 200, prop: "sourceNetwork", title: "Source Network" },
        { prop: "targetNetwork", title: "Target Network" },
        { prop: "amount", title: "Amount" },
        { prop: "action", title: "Action" }
    ];

    return (
        <FGrid alignX={"center"} className="f-mb-1 withdrawals_container">
            <FTypo size={18} align={"center"} className={"f-mb-14 f-mt--7"}>
                WITHDRAWALS
            </FTypo>
            <FTable>
                <FHeader>
                    <th>
                        <FTypo size={18} align={"center"} className={"f-mb-14 f-mt--7"}>
                            Source Network
                        </FTypo>
                    </th>
                    <th>
                        <FTypo size={18} align={"center"} className={"f-mb-14 f-mt--7"}>
                            Target Network
                        </FTypo>
                    </th>
                    <th>
                        <FTypo size={18} align={"center"} className={"f-mb-14 f-mt--7"}>
                            Amount
                        </FTypo>
                    </th>
                    <th>
                        <FTypo size={18} align={"center"} className={"f-mb-14 f-mt--7"}>
                            with
                        </FTypo>
                    </th>
                    <th>
                        <FTypo size={18} align={"center"} className={"f-mb-14 f-mt--7"}>
                            with
                        </FTypo>
                    </th>
                </FHeader>
                <Datatable tableBody={[]} tableHeaders={tableHeads} rowsPerPage={10} />
            </FTable>
        </FGrid>
    )
}
